record_data.record_plain_text:
?SILVER STATE SOUTH INTERCONNECT, LLC, CONCURENCE CO-TENANCY SHARED FACILITIES AGREEMENT
This is to certify that Silver State South Interconnect, LLC (“Silver South Interconnect”) assents to and concurs with the Co-Tenancy Shared Facilities Agreement by and among, Silver State Solar Power South, LLC. Silver State South Storage, LLC and Silver State Interconnect, described below, and files this Certificate of Concurrence in lieu of filing the specified agreement.
Joint Tariff Name/Description: Co-Tenancy SFA, Silver State Sol., Silver State Stor., & Silver State Inter.
Designated Filing Company:
Silver State Solar Power South, LLC Designated Filing Company Tariff ID: Agreements (190)
Tariff Program: Federal Power Act Electric (Traditional Cost of Service & Market Based Rate) Public Utilities
Limitation to Incorporation by Reference: None (shall concur with all subsequent variations of agreement)
Silver State South Interconnect, LLC By its duly authorized official /s/ Julie Holmes Vice President Dated November 19, 2024
